export const coding = [
    `def fibonacci(n):
    sequence = []
    a, b = 0, 1
    while len(sequence) < n:
        sequence.append(a)
        a, b = b, a + b
    return sequence

n_terms = 10

fib_sequence = fibonacci(n_terms)

print(f"Fibonacci sequence up to {n_terms} terms:")
print(fib_sequence)`,
`n_terms = 10
print(f"Fibonacci sequence up to {n_terms} terms:")`
]
